    Normalise barcode counts

    normaliseCounts.Rd

    Normalise barcode counts within a DGEList object

    Usage

    normaliseCounts(dge, method = "CPM", threshold = 0)

    Arguments

    dge

    DGEList object containing raw barcode counts to be normalised

    method

    method of normalization. One of cpm, tmm, tmmwsp, upperquartile or rle. see edgeR::calcNormFactors()

    threshold

    Threshold to apply to counts before normalisation

    Value

    Returns a data.frame object containing normalised barcode counts

    Examples

    data(test.dge)
normaliseCounts(test.dge, method = "CPM", threshold = 0)
